Modification of the de_nuke, which is based on this version with some additions added by myself.Â 
[ https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=626513993 ]

The map is aimed at improving the gameplay of the map, but maintaining the CS:S atmosphere and aesthetics. Materials were used only from CS:S and HL2 assets. In addition to changes in geometry, the map has become lighter, HDR lighting has been smoothed out, the noise on the map has become quieter, bots now speak more accurate information about the position of the enemy.
